emergence.util

Class GameResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • emergence.util.GameResult

  • public class GameResult
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the result of a game simulation. This is needed to have a callback object for multithreading. The attributes are the output, game, level, winner and score.
